{"tid":132502,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"男子吸煙燒著床單惹禍 一家4口送院","createTime":"2017-02-24T01:11:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-24T09:20:50.000Z","uid":122,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5b9da9ba771d9c89958d8260ad99bfaca9a025ef","tid":132502,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T01:11:07.000Z","msg":"<strong>男子吸煙燒著床單惹禍 一家4口送院</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170224/large/1487882836_7822.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170224%2Flarge%2F1487882836_7822.jpg&h=fbc8dc96&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港仔深灣道11號雅濤閣4座一單位發生火警，凌晨約2時51分，一名41歲姓黎男子在房間床上吸煙，疑用打火機點火時，火舌燒著床單引起火警。男事主慌忙撲救及用嘗試用腳踩熄火種。<br />\n<br />\n消防員到場時，男事主及家人已將火撲滅，約20名居民自行疏散到地下安全地方。男事主救火時腳部燒傷出現水泡，其86歲及83歲父母，以及34歲菲傭吸入濃煙不適，同送院治理。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170224/56346532\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170224%2F56346532&d=Xx1rX%2BBWBBKZa4OSQyufSUbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=765955ca\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170224%2F56346532&h=d64c7cf4\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170224/56346532</a>"},{"pid":"a15e466f12c28ea76e01f6c94ecd0bf5cfb26c78","tid":132502,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T01:11:54.000Z","msg":"煙剷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c106fe4c92fd85325cf08018fc9bf246d3610f7","tid":132502,"uid":45148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T01:25:31.000Z","msg":"41歲(吸煙)"},{"pid":"cf80a76a500155f230ee26e8d18563be2d60c547","tid":132502,"uid":1882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T01:29:55.000Z","msg":"抵死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\